# /etc/hpm/channels — hpm channel subscription list (one channel
# per line; lines beginning with # are comments).
#
# Each entry C makes hpm refresh fetch <repo-base>/<C>/index.json
# and merge it into the local package database. Package entries
# carry a `channel` field tagging which channel they came from;
# hpm install pulls the tarball from the same channel.
#
# Default install subscribes to `main` only (per
# memory/project_nonfree_repo.md). Enable extra channels with:
#   hpm enable non-free-firmware
#   hpm enable non-free
#   hpm enable contrib
# Disable with:
#   hpm disable non-free-firmware
# List with:
#   hpm channels
main
